&lt;h1 id="submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft"&gt;Submit a final draft, not a first draft&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s not at all important to get it right the first time. It&amp;rsquo;s vitally important to get it right the last time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— Andrew Hunt and David Thomas, &amp;ldquo;The pragmatic programmer&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a corollary to &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/terencetao/writing-guide/en/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/"&gt;Proofread and double-check your paper before submission&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>